name: Holiday Necklace Gift Pack
description:
This is a build your own necklace! Chose any charm and any birthstone combo. Just add your choice to your purchase notes! 

This offer is good through December 1st! 

**components are sterling silver and swavorski crystal**

name: City and State Necklaces
description:
Your city you love on the heart of your favorite state all in one lovely pendant. These necklaces are a great gift for that best friend form back home or the student son or daughter to represent their college state. All kinds of people adore these custom necklaces. 


This awesome necklace comes in a nickel silver finish and can be ordered in any state you want! If you want the heart stamped where a specific city is please let us know at the time of purchase and we will gladly make it that way! Hangs on a 24 inch chain. If you'd like a different length please specify at the time of purchase. 


This item can also be made in copper as well as sterling silver or gold filled upon request. The price for silver with be different. 



** These are made to order and current processing time averages about 10 days before shipping. **

name: Sterling Silver State Ring
description:
These rings can be made in any state you like. Sterling silver base with a silver, copper or gold filled state shape. A heart can be stamped on your favorite city or it can be left plain. The options are endless! 

Sizes 6,7,8,9 available. 

Specify your state, city, size and metal color choices at time of purchase please.

name: Raw Herkimer Diamond and Peridot Cabochon Wrap Ring size 9-10
description: This is a one of a kind piece with two types of sparkle. A rough herkimer diamond point in it's natural beauty. And a round smooth cabochon of peridot in a crisp apple green hue. These two stones compliment one another on a wrap style ring setting that can adjust slightly to fit a range of sizes from 9-10 easily. The thicker band makes this a very sleek silver look with the stones as the main double feature.

name: Sterling Silver Amber and Turquoise Ring
description: Turquoise and amber compliment each other so perfectly in fancy bezel settings on this thick band. This style of ring is so unique. Perfect for gift giving because of size versatility. This ring fits from 9 to 10.5 easily and comfortably.
